social_posts.post_text: Happiest of birthdays 🎂 to my earthly Queen! Thankyou for being the best mommy and even better Grammy! Thankyou for being a true prayer warrior and loving me with no conditions. I wouldn’t have made it this far in life without you! I love you ❤️

Happy 1/2 Birthday to my Sonshine! ❤️ Time seriously flew and watching you grow and reach different milestones makes my heart smile. Your a little ball of sunshine and hearing you laugh makes me feel like I’m doing something right. I wish your grampy could meet you I just know he would have a song and nickname ready for you. I just know he would’ve loved you and you would’ve loved him! 🥹❤️ 
 
The legacy continues with you! As we celebrate life, trying new foods, and growth in all areas we reflect on memories and moments that led us here. 🫶🏽 I love you so muchhhh Son! ❤️
Life just isn’t the same without you here Daddy! So thankful for all the memories we’ve made! I miss you always, but miss you most during the holidays. ❤️ I love you forever

I had a beautiful time at the @curlsontherunway event! 

This event showcased some very talented designers whose work speaks for themselves! 💙 

Seeing the talented Melissa A. Mitchell @abeillecreations a Bahamian artist/designer work on stage touched me, knowing that our small country can produce such great talent! 🇧🇸

I cannot forget the goodie bags for each guest. Idk if it’s because I like new things or because the products and items were top quality but they definitly contributed to this event being a top tier experience. Definitely will give this event a 10/10 and will do it again.
